Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.93,0:01:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's more amazing than\NKamisakuramachi-Ginza.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.18,0:01:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know too\Nmany details myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there are lots of dangerous\Npeople around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.89,0:01:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I saw it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That black bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.97,0:01:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our first good target in\Na while, a teenage girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.93,0:01:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god for that info broker.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.20,0:01:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just then, I realized that\Nmy body was shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, is this truly "reality"\Nyou're looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The things you see every day\Nare the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, everyone,\Non passing your examinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.97,0:02:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan presently faces many problems:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a declining birthrate and increasing\Nclass stratification.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.69,0:02:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I look at your faces,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but feel that the future is\Nstill bright, that Japan is still all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, today is a special\Nday for all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:38.58,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}But I realize once again, as I stand here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you find yourself thinking that\Ntoday's a day just like any other?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:43.35,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}that it's a special day for us teachers, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ry-Ryuugamine Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A shy boy who'd just arrived in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoharo Anri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:03:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl who seemed a bit otherworldly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kida Masaomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may seem older,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm a fragile little fifteen-year old,\Njust like the rest of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One guy seemed to be enjoying\Nhimself massively.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamichika Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl with a dark side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably have a lot of people\Nlike this around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima Mika?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absent...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kind of scene you see every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Late on your first day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the middle of introductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Present yourself, right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagiri Seiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:04:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes, for no apparent reason at all,\Nyou can see the hint of another reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Yagiri... Get to your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'll be able to come\Nto school for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I may never come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just came to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yagiri, what do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an extremely important\Nmatter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to spend\Non you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yagiri, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A crack, suddenly appearing in your peaceful,\Neveryday life, throws you off guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,making you rethink things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's a girl here who\Nmay have seen exactly such a crack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two days ago, she should have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.18,Title1,,0000,0000,0000,,Highly
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.18,Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,Unpredictable
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:05:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was born in a normal household,\Nthe kind you can find anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She led a typical life without problems,\Nwithout difficulties.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when she started middle school,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it arrived at her doorstep,\Nsuddenly and without warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:18.04,SignA,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakura's Profile
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:18.92,SignC,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakura\N\NStuff just sucks.\NI want\Nto disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:20.29,SignB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nickname :
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:20.29,SignC,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakura\N\NStuff just sucks.\NI want\Nto disappear.\N\NLocation:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:20.29,SignD,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess my dad's having an affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was with another woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there was a letter, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Will you let him get away with this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt sent by someone\Nwho knew the woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad's in the wrong here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that guy's a jerk, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I decided that, for the time\Nbeing, I'd just hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, all the regular,\Neveryday moments
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of my life took on this awful tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like it was hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was only able to put up\Nwith it for six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured that things would be\Nbetter if my mom found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's hard to talk about,\Nyou don't have to force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things I don't\Nlike talking about, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:30.36,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}But how could you mistake a\Ncell phone for a remote control?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But nothing changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if my mom
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was keeping quiet, or if they had\Nworked it out away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's dumb jokes, the overly\Nsweet taste of Mom's stew...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of it changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I figured maybe I'd just disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,800)}Lately, that's all I've\Nbeen thinking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kinda the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as bad as you, Mazenda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:09.65,SignA,,0000,0000,0000,,To Nagura-san\N\NSubject:\N\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl I was dating...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad got her pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was my mother who\Nmade me the angriest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said it happens all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and since we have to consider our reputation,\Nnot to make it a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a word about how she felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured, maybe she was putting\Nthe family's reputation above me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe she was just thinking\Nabout my future and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.82,0:07:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't care about you, Nakura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She only cares about herself-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:08:02.60,SignE,,0000,0000,0000,,Mazenda-san, would you\Nlike to disappear with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mazenda-san, would you like\Nto disappear with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we die together,\Nmaybe they'll understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand what they truly\Nshould have cared about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking back, it was stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when she left,\Nthe girl was pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She felt a power in Nakura's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to see this person who felt\Nthe same things she felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it was a lie,\Nshe had nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or so she thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mazenda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you Nakura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The minute she saw his face,\Nshe thought it might not be Nakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:09:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason she went with him was that\Nshe thought she couldn't let herself run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So even when it happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one around at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:28.54,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}OK, then... Sorry for tricking you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprise, a desire to resist, regret...\NAll kinds of emotions came over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But right before she lost consciousness,\Nshe thought to herself
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that this was fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why should she care what\Nhappened to her any longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She would just vanish, without anyone\Nknowing what had happened to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there {\i1}is{\i0} someone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While she was unconscious,\Nthe world was moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like that hard a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without regard to her feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or her will...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good. I just can't get\Nthe money together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying I won't pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if anything happens to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all I'm saying is Shiki-san, of the\NAwakusu, won't be happy-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, I don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not busy, mind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet I'm only capable of wasting another\Ntwo and a half minutes of my life on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the other guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I don't need to tell a talented\Ntransporter like you how to do your job,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but all you need do is what you're asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kick 'em around a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world was moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things were changing, just a bit, from what\Nthe girl had thought was her "fate."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:55.92,SignF,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,350)}It read, "I've been asked\Nto take you to a certain place."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:08.03,SignG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,300)}I've been asked to take\Nyou to a certain place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.52,0:13:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bike moved silently. Though once in a\Nwhile, it made a noise like a horse's neigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like it wasn't real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what she felt was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl thought about the person\Non the other side of this warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.75,0:13:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were they thinking, what did\Nthey know, and how did they live?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they looked at her,\Nwhat did they see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.79,SignH,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone is waiting for you\Non this building's rooftop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:46.30,SignH,,0000,0000,0000,,This is as far as\Nmy job goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mazenda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really Nakura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Nakura who wants to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi... Were you the one who saved me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:14:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But how did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who had them kidnap you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I had you rescued, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were a bit angry at yourself\Nfor being scared
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you were kidnapped, despite the\Nfact that you had decided to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But had you resisted, that would've denied\Nthe part of you that wanted to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you thought you'd maybe accept\Nit as fate and give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that you've been saved,\Nyou find yourself relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see that look of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see the look on your face when\Nsomeone saw straight through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.82,0:15:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:16:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will sound a tad philosophical to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if I were to try to explain it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just love humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are the most interesting\Ncreatures there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, when I say I love humans,\Nthat means humans, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand your position?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of people have jumped from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so many as to call it really famous,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.49,0:16:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's high enough that\Nyou're certain to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See that stain down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you're special, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can live off simple honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a secret or two, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.37,0:17:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ever think about why it's OK for you\Nto keep secrets, but not for your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get straight to the point,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think everyone laughs at\Ndumb jokes and eats overly sweet stew,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,regardless of if they're having\Nan affair or know their spouse is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever their worries may have been,\Nnow they're just stains.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stains. Without exception, all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Equal before God...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to let go of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:18:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm just happy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I got to see your ugly feelings today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't your problems I'm\Nreally interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's how you are when you\Nworry about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you were just as I pegged you.\NReally quite boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you never intended to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun, Mazenda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She hesitated for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would she be able to hurt\Nhim by doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she thought that maybe she'd just\Nbeen waiting for an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe those words the man said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But without her knowledge...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:44.18,SignI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,500)}Because the world isn't\Nas bad as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And once again, she does\Nsomething extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl thought of her mom and dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of her dad and his lover,\Nand her mom and dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each of them had a part to their life\Nthat she didn't know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they weren't as stained with evil, hatred,\Nand self-interest as she'd thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they weren't obscured by\Ncompromise and weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,300)}As she looked for the way home,\Nshe thought of forgiving them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.49,0:20:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, the world\Nlooked different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every single person had\Ntheir own emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and every single person\Nhad their own secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She realized that this was normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where you wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you wherever, so buy me food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.65,0:20:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see... OK, how about a bookstore?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:57.75,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}There are a lot of bookstores around\Nhere. What are you going to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They seemed like the kind of\Npeople you'd see anywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:02.78,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Um, some manga to read when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she was sure they had\Nsecrets of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emotions they could never tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagiri-kun, something happened, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But you were absent on the first day...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.53,0:21:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said to leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a lady-killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That chick with the glasses\Nis in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just nervous about the dangerous\Nand risky life she's about to lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.15,0:21:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you try to speak Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What they're seeing may not be reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,200)}The girl thought to herself that maybe\Nshe'd also be able to tell someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1)}"The world isn't as bad as you think."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hear you'd turned into\Na defender of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.16,0:22:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought I'd asked\Na talented transporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.66,0:22:16.27,SignJ,,0000,0000,0000,,Were the others\Nwho jumped\Nalso your fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. The information broker,\NOrihara Izaya, isn't that evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not enough of a saint to stop\Nsomeone who wants to die, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun, talented transporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.55,0:24:15.01,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,This program is a work of fiction.\NAny resemblance to people, parties,\Nor situations is purely coincidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.01,0:24:29.94,Title3,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time\Non Durarara!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.01,0:24:29.94,Title4,,0000,0000,0000,,Rampant\NEvil
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.83,0:24:17.00,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikebukuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.00,0:24:19.23,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,He and she and I and you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.23,0:24:21.77,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come to this town looking for\Nsomething, seeking something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.77,0:24:24.61,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to change something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.61,0:24:25.20,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.20,0:24:26.55,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Rampant Evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.55,0:24:27.92,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Want sushi? It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.92,0:24:29.92,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, long time no see.
